## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on what makes a neighborhood good. The information is subject to the biases of the sources and may not reflect the latest trends or changes in neighborhood dynamics. Additionally, personal preferences and individual needs can significantly influence what one considers a "good" neighborhood, which may not be fully captured in the sources reviewed.